<p><span style="color: rgb(0,255,255)"><span style="font-family: Arial"><span style="font-size: 10pt"><strong>Thời gian v&agrave;o cửa</strong></span></span></span></p>
<p style="text-align: center"><span style="font-family: Arial"><span style="font-size: 10pt; color: black"><strong><img onload="ResizeImages(this) " height="448" alt="" width="717" src="http://mu.gate.vn/images/Editor/image/website/Su%20kien%20trong%20game/image081.jpg" /></strong></span></span></p>
<p><span style="color: rgb(0,255,255)"><span style="font-family: Arial"><span style="font-size: 10pt"><strong>Quy tắc li&ecirc;n quan đến việc v&agrave;o cửa</strong></span></span></span></p>
<p>&nbsp;</p>
<div style="margin: 0in 5.5pt 0pt 28.35pt"><span style="color: rgb(255,255,255)"><span><span style="font-family: Arial"><span style="font-size: 10pt"><strong>Người tham dự</strong></span></span></span></span></div>
<div style="margin: 0in 5.5pt 0pt 28.35pt"><span style="color: rgb(153,204,255)"><span style="font-family: Arial">&nbsp;</span></span></div>
<div style="margin: 0in 5.5pt 0pt 42.55pt"><span style="color: rgb(153,204,255)"><span style="font-family: Arial"><font size="2">1)</font><span style="font: 7pt 'Times New Roman'; font-size-adjust: none; font-stretch: normal">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span><font size="2">&iacute;t nhất l&agrave; 4 người&nbsp;~&nbsp;nhiều nhất l&agrave; 20 người v&agrave;o theo thứ tự trước sau.</font></span></span></div>
<div style="margin: 0in 5.5pt 0pt 42.55pt"><span style="color: rgb(153,204,255)"><span style="font-family: Arial">&nbsp;</span></span></div>
<div style="margin: 0in 5.5pt 0pt 42.55pt"><span style="color: rgb(153,204,255)"><span style="font-family: Arial"><font size="2">2)</font><span style="font: 7pt 'Times New Roman'; font-size-adjust: none; font-stretch: normal">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span><font size="2">Trong 24h mỗi người chỉ c&oacute; thể tham gia 6 lần.</font></span></span></div>
<div style="margin: 0in 5.5pt 0pt 42.55pt"><span style="color: rgb(153,204,255)"><span style="font-family: Arial">&nbsp;</span></span></div>
<div style="margin: 0in 5.5pt 0pt 42.55pt"><span style="color: rgb(153,204,255)"><span style="font-family: Arial"><font size="2">3)</font><span style="font: 7pt 'Times New Roman'; font-size-adjust: none; font-stretch: normal">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span><font size="2">Trong trường hợp kh&ocirc;ng đủ người theo y&ecirc;u cầu sẽ được đưa về Devias</font></span></span></div>
<div style="margin: 0in 5.5pt 0pt 42.55pt"><span style="color: rgb(153,204,255)"><span style="font-family: Arial">&nbsp;</span></span></div>
<div style="margin: 0in 5.5pt 0pt 42.55pt"><span style="color: rgb(153,204,255)"><span style="font-family: Arial"><font size="2">4)</font><span style="font: 7pt 'Times New Roman'; font-size-adjust: none; font-stretch: normal">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span><span><font size="2">C&oacute; thể v&agrave;o cửa th&ocirc;ng qua &ldquo;Mira ju&rdquo; ở tọa độ (224,52) Devias.</font></span></span></span></div>
<div style="margin: 0in 5.5pt 0pt 42.55pt"><span style="font-family: Arial">&nbsp;</span></div>
<div style="margin: 0in 5.5pt 0pt 42.55pt; text-align: center"><span style="font-family: Arial"><span style="color: black"><font size="2"><img onload="ResizeImages(this) " height="310" alt="" width="244" src="http://mu.gate.vn/images/Editor/image/website/Su%20kien%20trong%20game/image082.jpg" /></font></span></span></div>
<div style="margin: 0in 5.5pt 0pt 42.55pt"><span style="font-family: Arial">&nbsp;</span></div>
<div style="margin: 0in 5.5pt 0pt 42.55pt">&nbsp;</div>
<div style="margin: 0in 5.5pt 0pt 42.55pt"><span style="color: rgb(153,204,255)"><span style="font-family: Arial">&nbsp;C</span><span style="font-family: Arial"><span style="font-size: 10pt">&oacute; thể c&oacute; được th&ocirc;ng tin về con người hiện tại v&agrave; đền ch&ugrave;a đ&uacute;ng với cấp bậc character.</span></span></span></div>
<div style="margin: 0in 5.5pt 0pt 0.75in; text-indent: -0.25in">&nbsp;</div>
<div style="margin: 0in 5.5pt 0pt; text-indent: 0in"><span style="color: rgb(153,204,255)"><span style="font-family: Arial">&nbsp;</span></span></div>
